HEADWORD: Systolic
<hw>Sys*tol"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
systole, or contraction; contracting; esp., relating to the systole of
the heart; <as>as, <ex>systolic</ex> murmur</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Dunglison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

